<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <style>
        body, .body-wrap {
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #71bc37;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #71bc37;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer img {
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 150px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<table class="body-wrap">
    <tr>
        <td>
            <div class="container">
                
                <!-- Header -->
                <div class="header">
                    <h1>{{ subject }}</h1>
                </div>

                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="content">
                    <p>You have requested for the {{ subject }}. Please find the attached pdf</p>
                
                    
                    
                    <p>If this request was not made by you or you need further assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
                </div>

